Correct Answer

Black 1 and White 2 are the last defensive moves of the game.

::dia(#ch6_9_dia23) sz=13 vw=A5N13 base=none at=1 mv=J13D13 ab="C11 C12 D12 D9 E10 E11 E12 E13 E5 E6 E7 E8 E9 F11 F7 F8 G10 G5 G6 G9 J13 J5 J9 K10 K12 K13 K5 K6 K9 L10 L11 L12 L7 L8" aw="B11 B12 B13 C10 C13 C9 D10 D11 D13 D5 D6 D7 D8 F12 F13 G11 G7 G8 H10 H12 H13 H5 H6 H7 H9 J10 J11 J12 J6 J8 K11 K7 K8"
Correct Answer

Now, the last two neutral points, Black 1 and White 2, can be played.

::h2
