::h3
Answer 61

::dia(#ch7_1_dia1) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 mv=F13 ab="E12 F11 F13 G12 H12" aw="F12 G11 H11 H13 J12"
Correct Answer

By playing 1, Black can capture one white stone.

