How to Save Endangered Stones

::h2
Problem 71

::dia(#ch7_2_dia0) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 mv=N13F6 ab="E10 E4 E5 E6 E7 F5 F6 G6 G7 G9 N13" aw="D4 D5 D6 D7 E3 E8 F4 F7 G5"
Problem 71
Black to play

How should Black answer White 1?

::h3
Answer 71

::dia(#ch7_2_dia1) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 mv=F6 ab="E10 E4 E5 E6 E7 F5 F6 G6 G7 G9" aw="D4 D5 D6 D7 E3 E8 F4 F7 G5"
