Correct Answer 1

Black 1 to 3 and White 4 are the last points of profit left. The points marked A, called neutral points, have no value.

::dia(#ch7_10_dia5) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 mv=E6E13D13F13 ab="A7 B6 B8 C6 C9 D11 D12 D13 D2 D6 E1 E10 E12 E2 E3 E6 E7 E8 F11 F2 F4 F9 G10 G11 G4 H3 H4 J3 K4 L3 L4 M4 M5 N5 N6" aw="A5 A6 B1 B3 B5 C2 C5 D3 D5 E13 E4 E5 F12 F13 F3 F5 F7 F8 G12 G5 G6 G8 G9 H10 H11 H12 H6 J4 J5 K11 K5 L10 L5 L6 M6 M8 N7"
