Correct Answer

By playing 1, Black makes two eyes and lives. There is no other move if Black wants to live.

::dia(#ch8_dia2) sz=13 vw=A6N13 base=none at=1 mv=H10 ab="F11 F12 F13 G10 G12 H11 H12 H13" aw="E11 E12 E13 F10 F9 G9 H10 H9 J10 J11 J12 J13"
