Problem 168
Black to play

What happens in these two positions if Black moves first? White moves first?

::h3
Answer 168

::dia(#ch8_3_dia1) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 ab="E12 E13 E4 E5 F12 F3 F5 F6 G12 G13 G3 G4 G6 H12 H5 H6 J12 J13" aw="D12 D13 D4 D5 D6 E11 E3 E6 F11 F2 F7 G11 G2 G7 H11 H3 H4 H7 J11 J5 J6 K12 K13"
If Black Plays First

Black gets two eyes and life at both the top and bottom positions if he plays 1.

::dia(#ch8_3_dia2) sz=13 vw=A1N13 base=none at=1 ab="E12 E13 E4 E5 F12 F3 F6 G12 G3 G4 G6 H12 H5 H6 J12 J13" aw="D12 D13 D4 D5 D6 E11 E3 E6 F11 F2 F5 F7 G11 G13 G2 G7 H11 H3 H4 H7 J11 J5 J6 K12 K13"
