Correct Answer

Black 1 captures two white stones in a net. The two white stones cannot escape.

::dia(#ch9_3_dia8) sz=19 vw=A1K10 base=none at=1 mv=E6E4 ab="C4 C5 D6 D7 E6 E7 E8 F5" aw="B6 C2 C6 C8 D2 D5 D8 E2 E4 E5 F2"
Wrong Answer

Black 1 fails. White escapes with 2.

