::chapter(#ch9_4)

::h3
Snapback

::h2
Problem 201

::dia(#ch9_4_dia0) sz=19 vw=A13M19 base=none at=1 mv=M19H18 ab="E19 F18 G17 H18 J19 K17 K18 M19" aw="F19 G18 G19 H16 H17 J18"
Problem 201
Black to play

Capture three white stones with a snapback.

::h3
Answer 201

