Correct Answer

If Black plays 1, the three white stones are as good as captured. If White captures Black 1, Black recaptures four stones with a snapback.

::dia(#ch9_4_dia2) sz=19 vw=A13M19 base=none at=1 mv=E18H18 ab="E18 E19 F18 G17 J19 K17 K18" aw="F19 G18 G19 H16 H17 H18 J18"
Wrong Answer

If Black plays 1, he fails. White connects with 2 and his stones cannot be captured.

::h2
